The work printed With this title and found in many MSS. is not by Bede, but by Florus Lugdunensis The genuine work does, however, exist in MS. ; one MS. 15 at Troyes, according to Giles, Opp. xii. pp. x—xii; another is at Monte Casino, No. 178 (see Bibliotheca Oasinensis, vol. iv, under that number, where also an edition of it is promised, Which, as far asI know, has not yet appeared 2).
